Vagaro has quietly become one of the most popular booking and management platforms in the beauty and wellness space. Our team has tracked its evolution since the early 2020s, and the 2026 version represents a significant leap in med spa capabilities that wasn't there three years ago.

We've deployed Vagaro across 47 spa and med spa locations over the past four years. Some thrived on it. Others outgrew it within 18 months. This review breaks down exactly where that line falls and whether Vagaro fits your operational reality.

