- Med spas with 50% or less medical aesthetic services
- Small chains (2-5 locations) with centralized ownership
- Operators prioritizing cost control over enterprise features
- Businesses wanting built-in consumer marketplace exposure

**Not ideal for:**
- Multi-location franchises requiring granular unit economics
- Pure-play med spas with complex clinical workflows
- Operators needing extensive third-party integrations
- Businesses processing $100K+ monthly needing negotiated rates
