<h2 id="vagaro-vs-alternatives">🔄 Vagaro vs. Key Alternatives</h2>

**Vagaro vs. MindBody:** MindBody offers stronger multi-location controls and enterprise reporting but costs 2-3x more at scale. Choose MindBody for 10+ locations; choose Vagaro for cost-conscious growth under that threshold.

**Vagaro vs. Boulevard:** Boulevard provides superior client experience and luxury positioning but requires significant implementation investment. Boulevard fits high-end med spas charging premium prices; Vagaro serves the broader market.

**Vagaro vs. GlossGenius:** GlossGenius wins on design and simplicity for solo providers but lacks the depth for multi-provider operations. Vagaro is the clear choice once you have 3+ service providers.

